Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:58.77,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Even though it's easy to say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.99,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}when you stand in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:08.13,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}my personality stands up and gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.92,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I can usually pull through with my assertiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:16.47,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that's just how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:22.68,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}But no matter how hard I try, I can't break the wall that's between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:26.19,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I want you to realise… my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:29.81,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}So I always send a gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.73,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}of "I really love you" your way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.86,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}with all of my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:41.01,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}My flimsy silky heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:44.33,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}After meeting you, I finally realised
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:49.93,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that I'm really clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.20,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}The scars from love that I'd almost forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:58.76,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}have started to ache all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:02.35,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Someday, like how I normally would...
