Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are your feelings of guilt gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Kushieda-senpai is acting weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's a weird person by nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's been spacing out a lot more than usual recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the big year-end sale is coming up soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then spring cleaning is after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the deepest parts of the cupboards to the tatami mats,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean every inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking about it wrong; it's Christmas. Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to be good for the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he's probably near the skies of Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa! Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that, I'll help you carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be great if he visits our house again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}love{\i0} Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you love Christmas, but why so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need a reason to love Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The street decorations are sparkling beautifully...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and everyone is smiling and happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you'll spoil your dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, that's why I'm only eating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to celebrate the end of your suspension tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, yellowtails are a natural product, so they're really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least pretend to appreciate them because of the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellowtail hotpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of yellowtails, yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get closer to Minorin during my suspension?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No progress at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what did you do with the chance I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it couldn't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda won't come to the meeting place in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'll eat lunch with some other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after school, she's busy with club{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"With all that waiting, do you think you're the faithful dog, Hachiko?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you really think Minorin will come for you if you wait long enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fool. Stupid. Dumb dog. Idiot Ryuuji."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I was planning to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already said it all out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess not progressing at all is something that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll come up with a plan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas, so I'll be reborn as an angel of love to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you want, I'm a living saint right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint? I thought you were an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, I meant angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to give everyone a happy and joyful Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to take off one or two\Npieces of clothing, or even take it all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do I look like an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the crumbs are falling onto your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Get them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-san is back at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-san, we appreciate your effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We became your fans after we saw that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle between the boss and the Palmtop Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was actually your victory, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought the first and final battle against her for your love...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you found out she's going to study abroad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fight was very difficult and caused a lot of hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the last person standing was the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the true victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My tense thigh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my shaking calf...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.32,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I'm back at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop singing weird songs and give me a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! I'm a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I missed you a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wait for us at the meeting place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I overslept so I had to rush here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my thighs are so sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how did I get here before you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were surrounded by some weird guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kushieda{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did I make a bad joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin', Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taiga, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda broke down again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should seriously become a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me be bald for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a high school girl like you wearing a bald wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kitamura-kun, good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.10,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, good morning to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning, that's why I'm saying "good morning".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean your pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...full of admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am full of admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings for Aisaka can't be shown by just kneeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is why I'm lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of who it's for, you shouldn't fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't forgive someone, you have to talk to me about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's an assistant professor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I saw him coming out of a casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that confirms it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't late for the date because of his work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but because he was playing slot machines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so I messaged one of my girlfriends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was being treated badly by him, I asked her what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I found out something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a breathtaking development...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there's no such occupation as an "assistant professor".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only "assistant teacher".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he was lying about his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, I haven't heard a thing from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to make our teacher cry, Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend we don't know it's actually Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.75,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cheering For Your Love" was brought to you by Kitamura Yuusaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.05,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,the God of Broken Hearts.{3 liner split - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:01.67,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guest today goes by the pseudonym of Y-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God of Broken Hearts? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, because of that confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura has become the school's love saint{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he became a religious figure for those wanting to confess to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Kitamura will take all the bad luck away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something like "The Lucky God of Broken Hearts Legend".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:21.44,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me remind you, final exams are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do the people of our school love to believe legends so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.47,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:28.73,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the God of Broken Hearts, should also start studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this broadcast is really annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:31.63,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,but not everything goes my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he bring up the topic of studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't the title be "Cheering For Your Love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga is listening to it, so shut up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else she won't be able to hear the touching stories of Master Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, are you all right? Can hear it clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Taiga is being really modest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she would've killed Haruta had he done that any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm being good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm being good because it's nearly Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look, Santa is watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you think Santa really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Chi', it's nearly Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're naughty, Santa won't visit your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something strange about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen during your suspension?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this a sign of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to die tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I going to die tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.86,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.01,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the dreaded exams, it'll be Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time that everyone's looking forward to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now an announcement from the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the ceremony on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be a Christmas party in the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come as couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troubled by love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't ask him or her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try to invite the person you have feelings for to the party on that romantic night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.97,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.18,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,...Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}have{\i0} to invite Minorin to the Christmas Eve party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Huh?" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to confess to her in a snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're asking for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the holy Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the angel of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the holy child of Christmas and the model for being good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Santa is looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make your love life successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become Cupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like Cupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My god, aren't you slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The special party for cool guys is in here...{Oh, its the first instance of "coal", "ikemen" is pretty close to "cool guy" - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, god! Look, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy over there is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine with that type of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of time left, so if you're hungry, eat this first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas, and I'm waiting for you to do fun things to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, let's do fun things together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want a cuter and prettier Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Haruta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I the most unfortunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's talk about the real party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to decide who will be staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you love Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If everyone's asking me to go for it, I guess I'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come join me, you sugary-slug-dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what type of dog did you say I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, come join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not in the mood to go to a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not the time for me to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up unbelievably during the softball match,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we lost because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go and have fun at a party during a time like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the club members will look up to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have to practise for a match I have after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't need to help out, just come for the party and{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll help you guys set stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan, you're going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll heat it up using the power of Class 2-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make this clear, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your best interest to be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of plan is my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll determine whether the party will be a success or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's also up to me to get {\i1}that{\i0} unhappy somebody to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we'd be glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuu-chan, you're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan is going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, to study for our finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're meeting Kitamura and the others at the restaurant we always go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a salmon fillet in the frying pan,\Nremember to heat it up before you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ya-chan will be giza lonely gansu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with that "giza" and "gansu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a popular saying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some new person at work told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people say things like "gansu",
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "giza" sounds cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-chan is giza-ly smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.28,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds really wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it sound wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is giza-ly good! It's tera-ly correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.96,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan, take care of Yasuko for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:55.84,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a rebellious reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Inko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your cute and honest side?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the book you borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never cook you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prize I got at the cultural festival for winning the Mr. Lucky Guy contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it "The Boss's Notes".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be nothing to be afraid of if we use this to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest, this belongs to Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She let me win with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she can't come because of her job, so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit living in the past like an old person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not living in the{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, stop standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to study at the place where Minorin works,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should try and have a chat with her before everyone arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda took the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're ready to order, press the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Minorin is avoiding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why would she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't speak to each other at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was the one who invited her to the study session.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you told me to leave everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys even talk to each other at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Going to work" was an excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she said she's not going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's feeling down because she screwed up during a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your specialty to make everything better in times like these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how to support her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with Minorin seems different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you guys were more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Takasu and Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing a winter coat on cold days makes you really warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo, you should buy one for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want a copy of The Boss's Notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't study by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this table is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Taiga, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta, go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara, you're sitting next to Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sit next to Haruta, and Kitamura, you're sitting at the other table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I want to sit there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls should sit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Taiga? Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not want to sit next to Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's order now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to the drink bar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in everyone getting up for drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll get them for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want something hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, go to the drink bar with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cold today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you pairing Taiga and Kitamura up on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we've been found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I want you to help out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kitamura and Taiga would make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kitamura is probably still upset about the Boss rejecting him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think a new love would help cure him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga likes Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprised, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're the closest one to her since you take care of her and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so being surprised is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, it seems you really like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga likes Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I known that for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.32,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it would be good for Taiga and Maruo to go out with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it'd be too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! You agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone says it, it's not like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Taiga goes out with Maruo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't think it'll be interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says you're gentle, and you love to care for others,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.09,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you actually like Taiga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll support you, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you like Kitamu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop annoying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some super confusing Guns N' Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get your spirits up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have to come to the party, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be my usual self anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
